<br>
i did the twisted evil quest (the one from necht) you have to kill 2 cutthroat vines fill some vials. kill a named barkstripper then pour the vials of elixir on some rocks. when my BM did the quest i got a necklace with  7 quick/dex and  2 stealth when my ranger did the quest he got a 90 something af helm with  4 or 5 bow and other nice ranger stats.<br>
<br>
when i did the bracer quest (the one that requires you to get good faction at krrzack town and kill corrupters) my ranger received a bracer with thrust resist and  2 stealth (among other things) my friends hero received a bracer with slash resist more tank worthy stats. guess which one my BM got?<br>
<br>
can any one mention this to the powers that be? BM's need a little love too if your not going to make BM specific gear at least let us get generic TANK gear instead of making us feel like a ranger minus the stealth, self buffs and bow. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thedunner>TheDunner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#000000>(1/2/03 10:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Blademaster rewards for SI quests</span><hr size=1> Killing Ixthiar Broodmothers can net a couple of nice rings that are relevant to a blademaster.  They're not OTD or quest specific.  (There's an associated quest, but you can get the rings without doing the quest)  <br>
